sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant NG as Nginx
    participant BE as Express Backend
    participant DB as MySQL

    Note over U,DB: User Registration Flow
    U->>FE: Enter name, email, password
    FE->>NG: POST /api/auth/register
    NG->>BE: Proxy to backend:5000
    BE->>BE: authLimiter (10 req / 15 min)
    BE->>BE: validate(registerSchema via Zod)
    BE->>DB: Check if email exists
    DB-->>BE: null (no conflict)
    BE->>BE: bcrypt.hash(password, 12 rounds)
    BE->>DB: INSERT user
    DB-->>BE: User record
    BE->>BE: generateAccessToken(JWT)
    BE->>DB: Store RefreshToken (7-day expiry)
    BE-->>NG: { user, token, refreshToken }
    NG-->>FE: Response
    FE->>FE: localStorage.setItem("chronicles-token", token)
    FE-->>U: Redirect to Dashboard
